        "title": {
          "type": "text",
          "$t": "Starý Orgoň na Kýčere"
        },
        "content": {
          "type": "html",
          "$t": "<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\nStarý Orgoň je postava, ktorá nás sprevádza na tejto stránke už od jej vzniku. Jej pôvod je v starej <a href=\"http://www.hradiska.sk/search/label/Legenda%20o%20Orgo%C5%88ovej%20K%C3%BD%C4%8Dere%20-%20Marikov%C3%A1\" target=\"_blank\">legende o poslednom pohanskom vladykovi</a>, ktorý sa so svojimi prívržencami uchýlil hlboko do ťažko prístupných hôr v srdci Javorníkov a tam odolával šíreniu novej viery. O to viac ma potešilo, keď som dostal pekný dar od mojej žienky - maľbu Starého Orgoňa na Kýčere. Autorom je Azraelangelo, ktorému týmto ďakujem za skvelo odvedenú prácu.&nbsp;</div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg_gwe6NepJGy4CNTFu0qLiBuFLtHrx4P-pIT0ET43bgO6kGLnXgzJ8XiCuslenF0B8sesNuuQpcQu7jneSEKLHjj6JD3MkwsMMuFNfYMOJWvbtgcIEMJMrFqsWQPMeJa36QiY7IqkhkN4/s1600/AzraelAngelo.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1600\" data-original-width=\"1200\" height=\"320\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg_gwe6NepJGy4CNTFu0qLiBuFLtHrx4P-pIT0ET43bgO6kGLnXgzJ8XiCuslenF0B8sesNuuQpcQu7jneSEKLHjj6JD3MkwsMMuFNfYMOJWvbtgcIEMJMrFqsWQPMeJa36QiY7IqkhkN4/s320/AzraelAngelo.jpg\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\nProstredie a najmä \"runové\" skaly s vytesanými tajomnými znakmi sú autentické a nakreslil ich podľa ich skutočného zachovaného vzhľadu, aký je možné pozorovať aj v súčasnosti.&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjfwNV85cWsyNwa9gR63gnxBXViegNevmxsXHdGfBK2RMedPiBwMhBgnYHziYPkK2BkNEf4BUId2ICJeLDxhDaNYGCneI0UA53zEZaIpAAQSyGQ9ZiSrIBjLTFkss7kEWlJ_hTwVOMpiKw/s1600/19.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1065\" data-original-width=\"1600\" height=\"213\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjfwNV85cWsyNwa9gR63gnxBXViegNevmxsXHdGfBK2RMedPiBwMhBgnYHziYPkK2BkNEf4BUId2ICJeLDxhDaNYGCneI0UA53zEZaIpAAQSyGQ9ZiSrIBjLTFkss7kEWlJ_hTwVOMpiKw/s320/19.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhYN91-NThg3fkOYR125pH9uJuV0FPp-pn7u2mSqboGpki89me7jnvdOproWZdIKvECU1JoCcJaU6vX59N8Bjz6EGrp7Hk7nAbQ3-LV9Rkc6fzkYlBkMGY-h8WTxe_BjpMGQq-ET6_Megg/s1600/20.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1049\" data-original-width=\"1600\" height=\"209\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhYN91-NThg3fkOYR125pH9uJuV0FPp-pn7u2mSqboGpki89me7jnvdOproWZdIKvECU1JoCcJaU6vX59N8Bjz6EGrp7Hk7nAbQ3-LV9Rkc6fzkYlBkMGY-h8WTxe_BjpMGQq-ET6_Megg/s320/20.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi_zXnIof6cBkw2jKAgPSfi4DLwEQRJM_gAjnqnavWfzKqDzZ92AcmlCP9sbn20tdNcsnNdJlG48vICBd_kkB1Sfao60AIEqaMsvY6xKv1dzeWdYW9F35PfBKSGuL33mArtP4mVfcTBKT8/s1600/21.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1072\" data-original-width=\"1600\" height=\"214\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi_zXnIof6cBkw2jKAgPSfi4DLwEQRJM_gAjnqnavWfzKqDzZ92AcmlCP9sbn20tdNcsnNdJlG48vICBd_kkB1Sfao60AIEqaMsvY6xKv1dzeWdYW9F35PfBKSGuL33mArtP4mVfcTBKT8/s320/21.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n"
